Shady Shovel 4 1 - 2

Normal effects

Damage: 4
If the Enutrof possesses Treasures:
- Steals 200% of the damage inflicted
- Consumes Treasures

Critical effects

Damage: 5
If the Enutrof possesses Treasures:
- Steals 200% of the damage inflicted
- Consumes Treasures
